Description:
    Explain the generator

Example:
    rails generate phonify User --app-name=monthly --app-key=AAA --api-key=BBB

    This will create:
        db/migrate/{timestamp}_create_phones.rb
        db/migrate/{timestamp}_create_messages.rb
        db/migrate/{timestamp}_create_subscriptions.rb

    Will add to
        app/models/user.rb

            has_one :monthly_subscription, as: "owner", class_name: "Phonify::Subscription", conditions: { app_id: Phonify.config.monthly }

    Will add config
        config/initializers/phonify.rb

            # app settings
            Phonify.config.monthly = 'AAA'
            # API authentication
            Phonify.config.api_key = 'BBB'
